5-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanswer%20our%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20November%2010%20and%20November%2013.%20Naturally%2C%20this%20unscientific%20survey%20is%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20BLS'%20usual%20heroic%20efforts%20to%20gather%20price%20data%2C%20but%20it%20can%20at%20least%20give%20a%20sense%20of%20how%20everyday%20shoppers%20are%20feeling%20about%20their%20wallets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20asked%20about%20whether%20people%20saw%20price%20changes%20in%20the%20last%20month%20or%20two%20for%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E10%20categories%2C%20and%20about%20200%20readers%20filled%20out%20the%20survey%20at%20least%20in%20part.%20This%20chart%20shows%20how%20many%20said%20they%20saw%20a%20price%20hike%20in%20each%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FSJBhQ%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Price%20survey%20results%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22487%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20responded%20with%20observations%20about%20how%20prices%20have%20shifted%20over%20a%20longer%20period%2C%20so%20the%20chart%20below%20reflects%20any%20mention%20of%20a%20rise.%20We%20excluded%20responses%20that%20were%20unclear%20or%20were%20not%20applicable%2C%20with%20some%20exceptions.%20For%20each%20category%2C%20that%20resulted%20in%20between%2090%20and%20around%20200%20usable%20responses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20respondents%20said%20they've%20noticed%20a%20rise%20in%20grocery%20and%20dining%20out%20prices%2C%20with%20one%20person%20calling%20dining%20out%20a%20luxury%20and%20another%20saying%20it's%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20do%20so.%20Some%20respondents%20specifically%20called%20out%20the%20cost%20of%20meat.%20A%20higher%20share%20of%20applicable%20respondents%20noticed%20an%20increase%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-coffee-is-more-expensive-roasters-cafe-owners-prices-tariffs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoffee%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20in%20alcoholic%20beverages.%20Some%20said%20gas%20prices%20fluctuate%2C%20so%20less%20than%20half%20said%20they've%20noticed%20a%20rise.%20Not%20many%20Americans%20noticed%20a%20rise%20in%20their%20rent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESurvey%20respondent%20Jeni%20Garcin%20said%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20have%20noticed%20price%20increases%20for%20tires%2C%20coffee%2C%20and%20many%20other%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20frustrating%20that%20people%20like%20us%20who%20are%20financially%20responsible%2C%20who%20are%20doing%20everything%20right%2C%20are%20still%20just%20feeling%20like%20we're%20stretched%20every%20step%20of%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Garcin%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarcin%20is%20cost-conscious%2C%20but%20she's%20not%20willing%20to%20cut%20out%20all%20expenses%3B%20she%20views%20coffee%20as%20a%20luxury%20%26quot%3Bself-care%20item%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20she's%20willing%20to%20pay%20the%20higher%20price.%20However%2C%20she's%20willing%20to%20opt%20for%20a%20cheaper%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-cheapest-cheeseburgers-fast-food-mcdonalds-wendys-burger-king-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eburger%20option%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20dining%20out%20or%20cut%20back%20on%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20sometimes%20I%20want%20the%20sour%20cream%20and%20onion%2C%20I%20look%20at%20the%20price%2C%20and%20I%20just%2C%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20all%20survey%20respondents%20mentioned%20a%20price%20change%20in%20groceries.%20One%20person%20said%20they're%20forgoing%20treats%20because%20things%20are%20too%20expensive%2C%20while%20another%20said%20they%20look%20for%20buy-one-get-one%20offers.%20One%20survey%20respondent%20said%20coupons%20aren't%20helping%20and%20that%20their%20standard%20list%20of%20groceries%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20in%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESurvey%20respondent%20Sarah%20DeVellis%20Adams%20said%20grocery%20prices%20have%20crept%20up.%20She%20thinks%20the%20cost%20of%20vegetables%20has%20been%20pretty%20stable%2C%20but%20thinks%20the%20cost%20of%20meat%20and%20processed%20foods%20has%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20absolutely%20affected%20our%20bottom%20line%20because%20the%20other%20things%20that%20are%20going%20through%20increases%2C%20we're%20forced%20to%20pay%20%E2%80%94%20utilities%20and%20things%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20way%20out%20of%20it.%20And%20so%20the%20only%20thing%20we%20can%20manipulate%20is%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexpensive-family-grocery-bill-teens-helped-save-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrocery%20budget%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20it%20gets%20harder%20and%20harder%20the%20more%20things%20cost.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeVellis%20Adams%20said%20her%20family%20doesn't%20dine%20out%20often%20because%20it%20has%20become%20unaffordable%2C%20adding%20that%20one%20outing%20can%20add%20up%20to%20an%20entire%20week%20of%20food%2C%20so%20she%20would%20rather%20use%20the%20money%20for%20groceries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20survey%20takers%20were%20so%20put%20off%20by%20prices%20that%20they%20would%20rather%20not%20dine%20out%20anymore.%20Year-over-year%20consumer%20price%20index%20data%20up%20to%20September%20showed%20prices%20have%20been%20rising%20faster%20for%20food%20away%20from%20home%20than%20for%20food%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPet%20owners%20are%20also%20finding%20they're%20spending%20more%20to%20feed%20their%20furry%20friends.%20Some%20respondents%20said%20there's%20been%20double-digit%20growth.%20Consumer%20price%20index%20data%20showed%20prices%20for%20pet%20food%20and%20treats%20increased%200.5%25%20in%20September%20from%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20much%20smaller%20than%20the%20increases%20in%202022%20when%20inflation%20was%20sky%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20two-thirds%20of%20people%20said%20they%20have%20seen%20a%20change%20in%20toiletries%20and%20personal%20care%20products.%20Some%20of%20them%20said%20paper%20products%20have%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20survey%20respondents%20called%20out%20or%20alluded%20to%20shrinkflation%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-food-prices-smaller-portions-restaurants-grocery-stores-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eitems%20have%20shrunk%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20not%20the%20price%2C%20or%20felt%20like%20prices%20have%20jumped%2C%20but%20quality%20has%20worsened%2C%20such%20as%20for%20clothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20asked%20survey%20takers%20if%20they%20had%20experienced%20any%20other%20notable%20price%20changes.%20Several%20people%20mentioned%20the%20cost%20of%20entertainment%2C%20repairs%2C%20and%20insurance.%20CPI%20data%20showed%20that%20the%20year-over-year%20increase%20in%20motor%20vehicle%20maintenance%20and%20repair%20remains%20elevated%20compared%20to%20pre-pandemic%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprices-food-coffee-gas-clothes-pets-rent-survey-inflation-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1764666724000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6924b822e1a9cbb014dedcde%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprices-food-coffee-gas-clothes-pets-rent-survey-inflation-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Most%20respondents%20felt%20that%20it%20has%20become%20more%20expensive%20to%20grocery%20shop%20and%20dine%20out.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Madison%20Hoff)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprices-food-coffee-gas-clothes-pets-rent-survey-inflation-2025-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22