%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there's%20a%20Gen%20Zer%20on%20your%20holiday%20gift%20list%20this%20year%2C%20it%20may%20be%20best%20to%20forego%20one%20of%20the%20quintessential%20young%20adult%20presents%3A%20a%20wallet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%204.4%20billion%20people%2C%20or%20about%20half%20of%20people%20worldwide%2C%20are%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmobile-wallet-payment-providers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20wallets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20that%20number%20expected%20to%20grow%2035%25%20by%202030%2C%20according%20to%20tech%20strategist%20firm%20Juniper%20Research.%20Adults%2024%20and%20younger%20are%20most%20likely%20to%20pay%20with%20their%20phones%2C%20using%20them%20to%20make%2045%25%20of%20their%20purchases%2C%20according%20to%20a%202025%20report%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20(across%20age%20groups%2C%20mobile%20phones%20were%20used%20for%2023%25%20of%20payments).%20Cash%20now%20accounts%20for%20just%2014%25%20of%20all%20purchases%2C%20and%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20used%20by%20people%20older%20than%2055%20or%20in%20households%20that%20made%20less%20than%20%2425%2C000%20a%20year.%20A%20McKinsey%20survey%20in%202024%20found%20that%20one%20in%20five%20people%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%20who%20use%20digital%20wallets%20often%20go%20out%20without%20bringing%20a%20physical%20one%2C%20and%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20only%2038%25%20of%20people%20ages%2018%20to%2024%20own%20a%20wallet%20or%20purse%20that%20they%20see%20as%20essential%20in%20their%20daily%20lives%2C%20according%20to%20Link%20Scheme%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20works%20to%20provide%20cash%20access%20in%20the%20UK.%20People%20are%20increasingly%20ditching%20cash%2C%20with%2030%25%20of%20Americans%20saying%20they%20haven't%20taken%20cash%20out%20of%20an%20ATM%20in%20the%20past%20month%2C%20and%2017%25%20saying%20it's%20been%20longer%20than%20six%20months%2C%20according%20to%20a%20LendingTree%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20shift%20is%20changing%20how%20they%20think%20about%20the%20money%20they%20spend.%20For%20older%20generations%2C%20cash%20feels%20real%3B%20for%20younger%20people%2C%20it%20might%20as%20well%20be%20Monopoly%20money.%20Hailey%20Moore%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20tells%20me%20she%20hasn't%20had%20a%20wallet%20in%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20and%20rarely%20carries%20cash.%20If%20she%20does%20get%20some%2C%20maybe%20in%20a%20birthday%20card%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20fun%20money%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20have%20cash%20on%20me%2C%20it's%20money%20that%20doesn't%20exist%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20And%20it%20disappears%20quickly.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20just%20use%20this%20to%20get%20myself%20a%20little%20treat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20younger%20shoppers%2C%20cash%20has%20lost%20its%20cachet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-wallet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20Pay%3C%2Fa%3E%20arrived%2011%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20people%20were%20slow%20to%20put%20their%20credit%20cards%20on%20their%20phone%3B%20tapping%20a%20phone%20didn't%20seem%20any%20better%20use%20case%20than%20swiping%20a%20credit%20card.%20That%20changed%20largely%20when%20contactless%20payments%20were%20favored%20in%20the%20pandemic%20and%20Apple%20Pay%20became%20easy%20to%20use%20when%20online%20shopping.%20Now%2C%20digital%20payments%20and%20cards%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20prioritized.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flast-penny-history-photos-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPennies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20each%20cost%20about%20two%20pennies%20to%20make%2C%20went%20out%20of%20print%20in%20November.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-set-up-your-passport-in-apples-digital-id-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDigital%20IDs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20now%20accepted%20at%20more%20than%20250%20US%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflyers-without-real-id-may-have-pay-to-clear-security-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eairports%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20domestic%20flights.%20More%20and%20more%20daily%20activities%20can%20be%20done%20with%20just%20a%20phone.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foura-ring-health-payments-digital-id-ceo-tom-hale-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOura%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20even%20looking%20into%20ways%20to%20make%20its%20smart%20rings%20work%20as%20wallets%20and%20keys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20digital%20wallets%20are%20used%20more%20frequently%2C%20people%20%26quot%3Btrust%20the%20digital%20wallet%20more%20than%20they%20trust%20cash%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Adam%20Gray%2C%20chief%20transformation%20officer%20at%20payments%20tech%20firm%20Stax%20Payments.%20They're%20more%20secure%20than%20carrying%20a%20physical%20wallet%20stuffed%20with%20cash%20and%20cards.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20trying%20to%20enable%20as%20many%20merchants%20and%20places%20to%20take%20it%20because%20it's%20better%20for%20everyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20people%20tend%20to%20spend%20more%20when%20paying%20with%20credit%20cards%20than%20cash.%20But%20that%20might%20be%20shifting%20among%20Gen%20Z%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcash-app-pay-expands-list-retail-merchants-in-superapp-bid-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECash%20App%3C%2Fa%3E%20survey%20published%20last%20month%20found%20that%2054%25%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20say%20they're%20more%20likely%20to%20spend%20cash%20thoughtlessly.%20The%20money%20that%20has%20already%20left%20your%20bank%20account%20or%20came%20in%20a%20card%20from%20your%20aunt%20might%20feel%20inconsequential%2C%20compared%20to%20growing%20numbers%20on%20a%20credit%20card%20statement%20that%20you'll%20have%20to%20face%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month.%20Moore%20also%20tells%20me%20that%20she%20mostly%20uses%20her%20debit%20card%2C%20only%20tapping%20a%20credit%20card%20for%20large%20purchases%20or%20those%20where%20she%20knows%20she'll%20earn%20points%2C%20like%20at%20gas%20stations%20and%20grocery%20stores.%20She%20mostly%20wants%20to%20build%20credit%2C%20and%20pays%20off%20the%20card%20early%20to%20avoid%20overspending%20what's%20in%20her%20bank%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShoppers%20have%20different%20feelings%20about%20using%20cash%20over%20cards.%20A%202023%20study%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Notre%20Dame%20found%20that%20people%20prefer%20to%20use%20cash%20on%20purchases%20they%20feel%20guilty%20about.%20But%20cards%20can%20also%20lead%20to%20quick-dopamine%20hit%20spending%20%E2%80%94%20researchers%20at%20MIT%20found%20that%20using%20credit%20cards%20can%20activate%20a%20reward%20pleasure%20sensor%20in%20the%20brain%2C%20driving%20people%20to%20become%20addicted%20to%20spending%20or%20at%20least%20lower%20the%20restraints%20to%20spending.%20(The%20researchers%20behind%20this%202021%20study%20did%20not%20look%20at%20contactless%20mobile%20payments%2C%20but%20did%20say%20that%20the%20ping%20that%20followers%20a%20purchase%20made%20on%20a%20phone%20could%20serve%20as%20a%20reminder%20of%20money%20spent%2C%20and%20disincentivize%20tapping%20with%20abandon).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20the%20first%20to%20throw%20your%20card%20onto%20the%20check%20at%20dinner%20and%20max%20out%20rewards%20has%20become%20appealing%20to%20travelers%2C%20but%20more%20young%20people%20are%20rapidly%20adopting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-now-pay-later-black-friday-risks-credit-score-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuy%20now%2C%20pay%20later%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecompanies%20like%20Klarna%20and%20Affirm.%20Last%20holiday%20season%2C%20Gen%20Z%20used%20BNPL%20services%20more%20than%20credit%20cards%2C%20according%20to%20research%20from%20J.D.%20Power.%20To%20the%20people%20who%20use%20these%20services%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20payment%20terms%20are%20just%20much%20more%20reasonable%20and%20transparent%20than%20credit%20card%20payment%20terms%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Sean%20Gelles%2C%20senior%20director%20of%20payment%20intelligence%20at%20J.D.%20Power.%20Frances%20Boyle%2C%20a%2029-year-old%20in%20Seattle%2C%20says%20has%20used%20buy-now%2C%20pay-later%20services%20on%20clothes.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20almost%20a%20way%20of%20justifying%20the%20purchase%2C%20because%20I'm%20like%2C%20'I%20can't%20spend%20over%20%24100%20right%20now.%20But%20%2420%20a%20month%2C%20that%20doesn't%20sound%20that%20bad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-salaries-at-payment-giants-visa-block-paypal-capital-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPayPal%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20that%20BNPL%20can%20lead%20people%20to%20spend%2091%25%20more%20at%20large%20businesses%20and%2062%25%20more%20at%20small%20businesses.%20Half%20of%20shoppers%20say%20they're%20more%20likely%20to%20complete%20a%20purchase%20when%20the%20split%20payment%20option%20is%20at%20the%20checkout.%20But%20a%20frictionless%20way%20to%20buy%20little%20things%20online%20now%20can%20turn%20into%20a%20pesky%20payment%20that%20lasts%20for%20months%2C%20and%20even%20barrel%20into%20a%20big%20debt%20down%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20might%20seem%20convenient%20to%20ditch%20cash%2C%20but%20a%20digital%20wallet%20can't%20cover%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETori%20Khutorna%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20who%20lives%20in%20Prague%2C%20says%20she%20doesn't%20own%20a%20wallet%20anymore%20%E2%80%94%20she%20uses%20a%20digital%20wallet%20and%20an%20app%20that%20houses%20her%20ID.%20It%20all%20started%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdowns%20with%20online%20purchases.%20%26quot%3BMoving%20on%2C%20I%20didn't%20see%20any%20real%20need%20in%20having%20cash.%26quot%3B%20But%20her%20plan%20has%20hit%20snags%20when%20traveling.%20Khutorna%20also%20says%20she%20had%20to%20ask%20a%20stranger%20for%20cash%20to%20buy%20food%20and%20then%20transfer%20her%20the%20money%20when%20she%20was%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20a%20major%20power%20outage%20took%20out%20a%20neighborhood's%20card%20payment%20options.%20Once%2C%20while%20in%20Italy%2C%20she%20couldn't%20buy%20a%20bus%20ticket%20because%20a%20card%20machine%20was%20broken.%20She%20was%20fined%20for%20not%20having%20a%20ticket%20(the%20fare%20enforcer%2C%20conveniently%2C%20had%20a%20device%20that%20allowed%20her%20to%20use%20Apple%20Pay%20to%20settle%20up%20her%20fine%20instantly).%20%26quot%3BSometimes%2C%20I%20feel%20really%20out%20of%20touch%20with%20reality%26quot%3B%20without%20cash%2C%20she%20tells%20me.%20When%20she%20sees%20a%20nice%20wallet%20for%20sale%2C%20she%20sometimes%20feels%20drawn%20to%20buy%20it.%20%26quot%3BThen%20I%20think%2C%20for%20what%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20young%20people%20saying%20goodbye%20to%20wallets%2C%20the%20world%20may%20soon%20have%20to%20catch%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Famanda-hoover%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EAmanda%20Hoover%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%20covering%20the%20tech%20industry.%20She%20writes%20about%20the%20biggest%20tech%20companies%20and%20trends.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-cash-joke-digital-wallets-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1764666547000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F692df64971107c9f34571ce6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-cash-joke-digital-wallets-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'It's%20money%20that%20doesn't%20exist%26quot%3B%3A%20Gen%20Z%20is%20treating%20cash%20like%20fake%20money.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ahoover%40insider.com%20(Amanda%20Hoover)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fge