Catching%20NATO's%20eye%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJoensuu%20once%20heavily%20relied%20on%20Russian%20tourism%2C%20an%20income%20flow%20sapped%20dry%20in%202022%20after%20the%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20prompted%20Finland%20to%20stop%20issuing%20tourist%20visas%20to%20Russians.%20The%20following%20year%2C%20Finnish%20authorities%20closed%20the%20country's%20833-mile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmap-how-russias-nato-border-expands-with-finaland-sweden-members-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eland%20border%20with%20Russia%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHelsinki%2C%20like%20much%20of%20European%20NATO%2C%20is%20now%20grappling%20with%20the%20question%20of%20how%20to%20guard%20its%20eastern%20borders.%20The%20Finnish%20government%20is%20already%20raising%20concerns%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvengeful-russia-sending-migrants-finland-to-punish-officials-us-deal-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eillegal%20immigration%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20it%20says%20Moscow%20is%20intentionally%20orchestrating%20as%20a%20gray%20warfare%20tactic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelluu%20was%20founded%20in%202018%2C%20well%20before%20these%20issues%20drew%20public%20concern.%20It%20began%20by%20building%20airships%20for%20civilian%20use%2C%20such%20as%20monitoring%20power%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20Kelluu's%20current%20user%20interface%20for%20monitoring%20airship%20fleets.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6927e97589026fbb4d0e8d52%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKelluu%20provides%20a%20digital%20user%20interface%20for%20monitoring%20airship%20fleets.%3Cp%3EKelluu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20war%20is%20turning%20it%20into%20a%20rising%20star%20in%20Europe's%20defense%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelluu%20was%20one%20of%2014%20firms%20picked