com%2Fgoodyear-blimp-nascar-daytona-flying-aviation-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%2421%20million%20Goodyear%20blimp%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20collapse%20if%20they%20were%20deflated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJanne%20Hietala%2C%20Kelluu's%20CEO%2C%20said%20that%20lighter-than-air%20technology%20is%20often%20overlooked%20in%20the%20defense%20industry%2C%20especially%20with%20disaster%20stories%20like%20the%20Hindenburg%20marring%20its%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224810%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20airship%20used%20by%20Israeli%20forces%20is%20seen%20docked%20near%20the%20ground.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6927e8f9e1a9cbb014df1d53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223206%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOther%20militaries%20have%20also%20deployed%20airships%2C%20though%20they%20are%20typically%20much%20larger.%20Israel%2C%20for%20example%2C%20deployed%20a%20large%20airship%20in%202024%20that%20it%20said%20was%20later%20hit%20by%20Hezbollah.%3Cp%3EChristopher%20Furlong%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENATO%20evaluators%20were%20surprised%2C%20he%20said%2C%20when%20they%20assessed%20the%20company's%20airships%20during%20trials%2C%20which%20included%20naval%20showcases%20in%20the%20Atlantic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20kind%20of%20believed%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Hietala%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20they%20looked%20at%20the%20specs%2C%20they%20were%20like%3A%20'Well%2C%20the%20wind%20is%20going%20to%20blow%20it%20away.'%20But%20when%20we%20actually%20deploy%2C%20they're%20like%3A%20'Oh%2C%20it%20actually%20works%20and%20makes%20sense.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelluu%20now%20maintains%20a%20small%20active%20fleet%20of%20just%20under%2020%20airships%2C%20but%20Hietala%20said%20it's%20focused%20in%20the%20near%20future%20on%20scaling%20up%20mass%20production%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20its%20airships%20are%20already%20being%20deployed%20in%20other%20countries%2C%20such%2