FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20government%20has%20signed%20a%20nonbinding%20letter%20of%20intent%20to%20invest%20up%20to%20%24150%20million%20in%20a%20chip%20startup.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ExLight%20is%20chaired%20by%20Pat%20Gelsinger%2C%20who%20ran%20Intel%20until%20his%20resignation%20late%20last%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20deal%20signals%20Washington's%20effort%20to%20regain%20leadership%20in%20chipmaking.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20government%20is%20poised%20to%20become%20a%20shareholder%20in%20a%20semiconductor%20startup%20chaired%20by%20Pat%20Gelsinger%2C%20who%20ran%20Intel%20until%20his%20resignation%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Commerce%20Department%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20Trump%20administration%20signed%20a%20nonbinding%20letter%20of%20intent%20to%20invest%20up%20to%20%24150%20million%20in%20xLight%2C%20a%20startup%20trying%20to%20build%20a%20more%20advanced%20and%20cost-effective%20way%20to%20manufacture%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investment%20would%20come%20from%20the%20CHIPS%20and%20Science%20Act%20and%20would%20be%20structured%20as%20equity%2C%20giving%20the%20federal%20government%20direct%20ownership%20in%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20%E2%80%94%20a%20first%20from%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20CHIPS%20Research%20and%20Development%20Office%20%E2%80%94%20signals%20Washington's%20effort%20to%20regain%20leadership%20in%20chipmaking.%20Most%20advanced%20semiconductors%20are%20manufactured%20outside%20the%20US%2C%20led%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-not-concerned-about-nvidia-ai-chip-gpu-asic-competition-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETSMC%20in%20Taiwan%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20Samsung%20in%20South%20Korea%20%E2%80%94%20areas%20where%20China's%20influence%20looms%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntel%20warned%20in%20July%20that%20it%20may%20halt%20development%20of%20its%20next-generation%20chip%2C%2014A%2C%20due%20to%20financial%20reasons.%20If%20Intel%20gives%20up%20on%2014A%2C%20this%20could%20be%20a%20death%20blow%20to%20US%20chip%20manufacturing%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fintel-us-chipmaking-nears-death-up-cutting-edge-chips-14a-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Alistair%20Barr%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%20in%20a%20July%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20far%20too%20long%2C%20America%20ceded%20the%20frontier%20of%20advanced%20lithography%20to%20others.%20Under%20President%20Trump%2C%20those%20days%20are%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Commerce%20Secretary%20Howard%20Lutnick%20in%20Monday's%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20partnership%20would%20back%20a%20technology%20that%20can%20fundamentally%20rewrite%20the%20limits%20of%20chipmaking.%20Best%20of%20all%2C%20we%20would%20be%20doing%20it%20here%20at%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Lutnick%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Palo%20Alto-based%20startup%2C%20founded%20in%202021%2C%20is%20developing%20free-electron%20laser%20technology%2C%20%26quot%3Ban%20alternative%20light%20source%26quot%3B%20for%20extreme%20ultraviolet%20(EUV)%20lithography%20machines%20that%20power%20cutting-edge%20chip%20production%2C%20the%20press%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ExLight%20said%20on%20its%20website%20that%20its%20systems%20would%20enhance%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffocus-breathing-before-big-presentation-asml-ceo-meditation-stress-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDutch%20firm%20ASML's%20machines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20undisputed%20global%20leader%20in%20EUV%20lithography%20systems.%26quot%3B%20EUV%20systems%20are%20only%20produced%20by%20ASML.%20xLight's%20technology%20will%20%26quot%3Btransform%20semiconductor%20fab%20capabilities%20and%20dramatically%20reduce%20capital%20and%20operating%20expenses%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-intel-ceo-pat-gelsinger-ai-bubble-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPat%20Gelsinger%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20was%20pushed%20out%20as%20Intel%20CEO%20late%20last%20year%20after%20the%20company%20struggled%20with%20weak%20earnings%20and%20fell%20behind%20in%20the%20AI%20chip%20race%2C%20became%20xLight's%20executive%20chairman%20in%20March.%20He%20is%20also%20a%20general%20partner%20at%20Playground%20Global%2C%20the%20venture%20firm%20that%20led%20xLight's%20%2440%20million%20Series%20B%20round%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGelsinger%2C%20who%20was%20CEO%20of%20Intel%20from%202021%20to%202024%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20CNBC's%20%26quot%3BSquawk%20Box%26quot%3B%20in%20October%20that%20Intel%20%26quot%3Bmade%20a%20set%20of%20bad%20decisions%20over%2015%20years%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20technical%20leadership%20wasn't%20%26quot%3Bled%20by%20technologists%20for%20many%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20late%20on%20AI%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGelsinger%20spent%20decades%20rising%20through%20the%20ranks%20at%20Intel%20and%20became%20one%20of%20the%20most%20influential%20voices%20behind%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchips-act-bill-to-boost-us-chipmaking-competition-with-china-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E2022%20CHIPS%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20landmark%20manufacturing%20legislation%20that%20reshaped%20America's%20chip%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ExLight%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20%26quot%3Bdrive%20the%20next%20era%20of%20Moore's%20Law%2C%20accelerating%20fab%20productivity%2C%20while%20developing%20a%20critical%20domestic%20capability%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gelsinger%20in%20a%20Monday%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-invest-xlight-chip-startup-former-intel-semiconductor-race-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17646533