s%20has%20launched%20a%20probe%20into%20Shein%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20selling%20unsafe%2C%20toxic%20products%20to%20US%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETexas%20Attorney%20General%20Ken%20Paxton%20said%20in%20a%20Monday%20news%20release%20that%20his%20office%20was%20investigating%20the%20fast-fashion%20giant%20for%20potential%20violations%20of%20Texas%20law%2C%20%26quot%3Brelated%20to%20unethical%20labor%20practices%20and%20the%20sale%20of%20unsafe%20consumer%20products.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaxton%20referenced%20Health%20Secretary%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr.'s%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrouble-in-maha-rfk-autism-doge-budget-cuts-medicaid-education-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMake%20America%20Healthy%20Again%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20campaign%20in%20the%20release%2C%20saying%20that%20safe%20and%20non-toxic%20products%20were%20a%20key%20ingredient%20in%20the%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20company%20that%20cuts%20corners%20on%20labor%20standards%20or%20product%20safety%2C%20especially%20those%20operating%20in%20foreign%20nations%20like%20China%2C%20will%20be%20held%20accountable%2C%26quot%3B%20Paxton%20said%20in%20the%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShein%20is%20headquartered%20in%20Singapore%20and%20sources%20many%20of%20its%20products%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTexans%20deserve%20to%20know%20that%20the%20companies%20they%20buy%20from%20are%20ethical%2C%20safe%2C%20transparent%2C%20and%20not%20exploiting%20workers%20or%20selling%20harmful%20products.%20I%20will%20not%20allow%20cheap%2C%20dangerous%2C%20foreign%20goods%20to%20flood%20America%20and%20jeopardize%20our%20health%2C%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPaxton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20said%20that%20the%20investigation%20will%20also%20examine%20Shein's%20data%20collection%20and%20privacy%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Shein%20representative%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20takes%20these%20concerns%20seriously%20and%20is%20%26quot%3Bfully%20committed%20to%20cooperating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20strive%20to%20operate%20responsibly%20across%20every%20area%20of%20our%20business%2C%20implementing%20policies%20designed%20to%20protect%20both%20our%20shoppers%20and%20those%20we%20work%20with.%20We%20welcome%20constructive%20engagement%20with%20Attorney%20General%20Paxton%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20representative%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20latest%20setback%20that%20Shein%20is%20facing%20in%20the%20US%2C%20its%20largest%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20start%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20second%20term%2C%20his%20administration%20has%20cracked%20down%20on%20the%20de%20minimis%20trade%20loophole%2C%20which%20previously%20allowed%20low-cost%20parcels%20to%20enter%20the%20country%20tax-free.%20Shein%20said%20in%20April%20that%20it%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshein-and-temu-raise-prices-in-8-days-because-tariffs-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eraise%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20account%20for%20higher%20operating%20expenses%2C%20a%20result%20of%20changes%20in%20trade%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaxton%2C%20who%20is%20running%20for%20Senate%20in%202026%2C%20is%20not%20the%20first%20government%20official%20globally%20to%20launch%20a%20probe%20into%20Shein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korean%20health%20officials%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshein-temu-shoes-11-229-times-legal-limit-toxic-substances-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eraised%20concerns%3C%2Fa%3E%20several%20times%20last%20year%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eabout%20Shein's%20products%20containing%20toxic%20substances%20above%20legal%20limits.%20In%20response%20to%20the%20probes%2C%20Shein%20told%20Singaporean%20outlet%20The%20Straits%20Times%20in%20June%202024%20that%20it%20had%20removed%20the%20offending%20products%20from%20its%20catalogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20the%20European%20Commission%20said